Name: Average time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Queued + Awaiting Assignment before transitioning to Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that include Completed + In Call compared to variants that end directly in Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time from case start until Queued + Awaiting Assignment is first performed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the subsequent occurrence of Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Cycle time of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in cases where Completed + In Call appears later in the trace
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total waiting time accumulated during Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants containing multiple occurrences of Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average time between consecutive occurrences of Queued + Awaiting Assignment within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Minimum time from Queued + Awaiting Assignment to Completed + In Call when both appear in the same variant
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that transition directly to Accepted + In Progress versus those that loop back to Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in high-performance variants (performance < median) versus low-performance variants (performance â‰¥ median)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time from the last Queued + Awaiting Assignment to the first Completed + In Call in multi-occurrence traces
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment grouped by country to assess regional handling delays before potential escalation to Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Completed + In Call in variants where no intermediate wait states (e.g., Accepted + Wait - User) occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
